title: Mid Tempo Bass Music Collection 2014
description:
This is a collection of the Best Midtempo Bass Music and Beautiful downtempo. A lot of this music is from 2014 including some new albums by Kaminanda and more.

Here is a list of artist:

Akara (2013) - The World Beyond [mp3-320]
eO - Nest Of Wishes (2012) [LAME MP3]
Erothyme - Circadia (vbr0)
Kaminanda - Liminal Spaces - MP3 320
SIXIS - Transhuman EP (320)
Subaqueous Immerge 320
Kalya Scintilla - The Remix Archives - Vol. 1
Subaqueous - Revision

Also includes some music by Biolumigen, Quanta, Somatoast, Mumukshu, Shwex and more.
